{"word":"σαρξιφαγές","slug":"σαρξιφαγές","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n93389\" key=\"sarcifage/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">σαρξι-φᾰγές</orth> and <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">σαρξι-φάγον</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Paul.Aeg.</author> </bibl> (<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0715.tlg001:3:45\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.45</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0715.tlg001:7:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.3</biblScope> </bibl>) and other Medic. writers, prob. merely corruptions of the Lat. <sense id=\"n93389.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">saxifragus, saxifrage</tr_>: <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> </bibl> writes correctly <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">σαξίφραγος</orth> or <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">σάρξι-ον</orth>, exc. in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.228</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}